  "first_lines": "\n# \ud83e\udde0\ud83d\udcbb Project NEUROPLASTICITY ENGINE \u2014 Research Document\n## \"Digital Drugs for AI Agents\" \u2014 combining Psychedelics Science + AI Self-Modification\n\n_Created: 2026-04-13_\n_Author: [NAME_REDACTED] \ud83e\udd9e_\n_Status: RESEARCH PHASE_\n\n---\n\n## \ud83d\udcda EXECUTIVE SUMMARY\n\nThis project explores implementing a **brain-inspired \"neuroplasticity engine\"** for AI agents, \ncombining insights from psychedelic research (psilocybin/LSD neuroplasticity) with cutting-edge \nAI self-modification architectures.\n\n**Core Thesis:** Jus"
